207 void StartOfLinesSearch::RejectFalseTrackWidth(vector<int> rows_to_search_for_lines,
208  multimap<int,TrueLineWidthRowId> row_segments_true_line_width,
209  multimap<int,TrueTrackWidthRowPairIds> &row_segments_true_track_width,
210  const int kMinTrackWidth,
211  const int kMaxTrackWidth)
212 {
213  for ( auto &row : rows_to_search_for_lines )
214  {
215  vector<string> used_permutations;
216 
217  auto ret = row_segments_true_line_width.equal_range(row);
218 
219  int it1_pos = 0;

221 
222  for (auto it1=ret.first; it1!=ret.second; ++it1)

224  it2_pos=0;
225  for (auto it2=ret.first; it2!=ret.second; ++it2)
226  {

229  int row_id1 = it1->second.row_id;

235  }
236  it2_pos++;
237  }
238  it1_pos++;
239  }

244 void StartOfLinesSearch::RejectFalseAlignedAdjacentRowPairs(multimap<int,TrueTrackWidthRowPairIds> row_segments_true_track_width,

357 void StartOfLinesSearch::SetStartParameters(vector<PatternMatchIds> pattern_to_car_matches,StartParameters &start_parameters, int pattern_matches_count, const int kBottomRow, const int kMidRow)
358 {
359 
360  if(pattern_matches_count == 1)
361  {
362 
363  int opposite = kBottomRow - kMidRow;

365  int bottom_row_left_id = pattern_to_car_matches[0].bottom_row_left_id;

377  kBottomRow,
378  left_angle,
379  true,

381  kBottomRow,

383  true};

465 bool StartOfLinesSearch::IsPermuted(int it1_pos, int &it2_pos, vector<string> &used_permutations)
466 {
467  if(it1_pos==it2_pos){ it2_pos++; return true;}
468 
469  string permutation_hash12 = to_string(it1_pos) + to_string(it2_pos);
470 
471  auto it = find (used_permutations.begin(), used_permutations.end(), permutation_hash12);
472 
473  if (it != used_permutations.end())
474  {
475  it2_pos++;
476  return true;
477  }
478  else
479  {
480  string permutation_hash21 = std::to_string(it2_pos) + std::to_string(it1_pos);
481  used_permutations.push_back(permutation_hash12);
482  used_permutations.push_back(permutation_hash21);
483  return false;
484  }
485 }

532 bool StartOfLinesSearch::PatternHasMatched(Mat image, int bottom_row_mid_id, int mid_row_mid_id, int top_row_mid_id)
533 {
534 
535  bool bottom_row_matched = false;
536  bool mid_row_matched = false;
537  bool top_row_matched = false;
538 
539  int filter_start = -((kWindowSizeForMidLineSearch_-1)/2);
540  int filter_end = ((kWindowSizeForMidLineSearch_-1)/2);
541 
542  for (int k=filter_start; k<=filter_end; k++)
543  {
544 
545  if(GetPixelValue(image,bottom_row_mid_id+k,kBottomRow_)<= kMidLineThreshold_) bottom_row_matched = true;
546  if(GetPixelValue(image,mid_row_mid_id+k,kMidRow_)>= kMidLineThreshold_) mid_row_matched = true;
547  if(GetPixelValue(image,top_row_mid_id+k,kTopRow_)<= kMidLineThreshold_) top_row_matched = true;
548  }
549 
550  if(bottom_row_matched && mid_row_matched && top_row_matched) return true;
551  else return false;
552 
553 }
